Shockwave:



Shockwave's single golden optic seemed to intensify in color at the bickering.

"You three will survey areas on this planet for us to make possible 
installations.  They should be able to receive sunlight, somewhat hidden, 
somewhere remote, and somewhere not to close to enemy installations.  From 
these points we can store energy or retreat to them if we are being pursued 
by enemies and are to far away from the Ramora."
